<HEAD>Britain Grounds 12 Boeing 737-400 Aircraft</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 5 grafs to UPDATE with FAA report, Boeing comment.
Picks up 3rd graf pvs, `On Friday ...'.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
